<h2 id="useful-plugins">Useful Plugins</h2>

<h3 id="conduit">Conduit</h3>

<p>Conduit enables you to connect from your local system to your remote backing<br />
service instances. This allows you to use the standard PostgreSQL and MySQL CLI<br />
tools to easily make backups and interrogate your backing services. For more<br />
information on how to implement this, check the <a href="https://github.com/alphagov/paas-cf-conduit/blob/master/README.md">Conduit README on<br />
Github</a>.</p>
